    "about.profiles.curator.name": "Kereybaeva Aigerim",
    "about.profiles.curator.role": "Scientific Curator / Teacher",
    "about.profiles.curator.bio": "Kereybaeva Aigerim is a chemistry teacher with international teaching experience and high-level training. Prize-winner of national competitions, including the 'Talented Teacher — Gifted Children' olympiad. Awarded the Certificate of Honor by the Ministry of Education and Science of the Republic of Kazakhstan for contribution to the development of education.",
    "about.profiles.curator.background": "Trained in the IB program (England, 2020), STEM, CLIL, and PISA courses. Actively engaged in mentorship, expert of the BEYIM AI platform and jury member of olympiads. Interests: project-based learning and development of students' research competencies.",
